EventFlow — Booking Confirmed

Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,

Your booking is CONFIRMED!

Booking Reference: <%= @booking.reference_code %>

Event:   <%= @event.title %>
Date:    <%= @event.start_at.strftime("%A, %B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %>
Venue:   <%= @event.venue.name %>, <%= @event.venue.city %>
Seats:   <%= @booking.seats.map(&:label).join(", ") %>
Total:   <%= @booking.total_amount.zero? ? "Free" : number_to_currency(@booking.total_amount, unit:"$") %>

View Booking: <%= booking_url(@booking) %>

You'll receive a reminder 24 hours and 1 hour before the event.

— EventFlow Team
